/></a> APT group: Operation Olympic Games</h3>\n<table width=\"100%\" class=\"tborder\">\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Names</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">Operation Olympic Games <i><font size=\"-2\">",
